00:00:47.190 --> 00:00:51.570
They may have started with the ancient Egyptians,
like the Bible notes a Pharaoh's birthday,

00:00:51.570 --> 00:00:55.430
although it's possible that could mean the
date of the Pharaoh's death, like the day

00:00:55.430 --> 00:00:57.329
