and New Zealand, you might find Fairy Bread,

00:01:33.659 --> 00:01:36.360
which is white bread, butter, and sprinkles.

00:01:36.360 --> 00:01:40.850
By the way, the round and colorful sprinkles
are called "hundreds-and-thousands" there.

